comments: VanVleet (TOR) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Allen's (BKN) path and absorbs the contact.
LeVert (BKN) makes contact to Siakam's (TOR) arm and affects his driving shot attempt.
Allen (BKN) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Anunoby's (TOR) path and absorbs the contact.
Siakam (TOR) retracts his off-arm from LeVert (BKN) as he releases from the contact on the perimeter.
Siakam (TOR) fumbles the ball and legally picks it back up and does not dribble again prior to his pass.
Allen (BKN) does not make contact with Siakam (TOR) during his pass attempt.
Harris (BKN) legally contests Siakam's (TOR) pass attempt.
LeVert (BKN) places and retracts his hands to the side of VanVleet's (TOR) body during his one-handed driving shot attempt.
Lowry (TOR) briefly engages and separates from Harris (BKN) during the rebound.
Allen (BKN) takes a step toward Lowry (TOR) as marginal contact occurs at the end of his drive and doesn't affect his ability to pass.
Powell (TOR) establishes himself in a legal screening position in Temple's (BKN) path and absorbs the contact.
Allen (BKN) firms up during the off-ball screen in Anunoby's (TOR) path and does not deliver contact.
Anunoby (TOR) does not release the ball on his shot attempt prior to the 24-second shot clock expiring.
Lowry (TOR) makes contact with Harris' (BKN) arm, causing him to lose control of the ball on the perimeter.
Temple (BKN) does not make contact with the ball once his body slides into the backcourt.

VanVleet (TOR) makes contact with Temple's (BKN) lower body that affects his ability to maintain his balance near the sideline. The contact occurs as he receives the pass and prior to his upward shooting motion.
